{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"hillshadeMethod"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNHillshadeStyleLayer(py)hillshadeMethod","title":"hillshadeMethod","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"hillshadeMethod","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnhillshadestylelayer\/hillshademethod"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"hillshadeMethod"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is an expression that evaluates to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"standard","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Set this property to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to reset it to the default value."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Constant "},{"code":"MLNHillshadeMethod","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any of the following constant string values:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"standard","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":": The legacy hillshade method."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"basic","type":"codeVoice"},{"typ